Cell["\<\
En la l\[IAcute]nea recta del medio hay que indicar que hay \
bifurcaci\[OAcute]n trasncr\[IAcute]tica, en el \[AAcute]rea naranja hay que \
indicar que hay dos bifurcaciones de silla-nodo, y en el \[AAcute]rea azul \
indicar que no hay bifurcaciones.
Un espacio de par\[AAcute]metros m\[AAcute]s completo, que resultar\[IAcute]a \
en puntos extra, ser\[IAcute]a hacerlo como hicimos en clase, indicando \
cuantos puntos de equilibrio hay y qu\[EAcute] bifurcaciones ocurren. Esto \
ser\[IAcute]a de la siguiente forma\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9102732245180006`*^9, 3.91027332472212*^9}, {
  3.91027337689439*^9, 
  3.9102733790768547`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"554af68d-9f7f-4559-a354-\
c39e7563b4cb"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"RegionPlot", "[", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"h", ">", "0"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"(", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"h", "<", "0"}], "&&", 
       RowBox[{"h", "<", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"-", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"r", "^", "2"}], ")"}]}], "/", "4"}]}]}], ")"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"(", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"h", "<", "0"}], "&&", 
       RowBox[{"h", ">", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"-", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"r", "^", "2"}], ")"}]}], "/", "4"}]}]}], ")"}]}], "}"}], 
   ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"r", ",", 
     RowBox[{"-", "2"}], ",", "2"}], "}"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"h", ",", 
     RowBox[{"-", "2"}], ",", "2"}], "}"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"FrameLabel", "->", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"r", ",", "h"}], "}"}]}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"PlotPoints", "->", "100"}]}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.910273394004058*^9, 3.91027342488193*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[13]:=",ExpressionUUID->"b9043a79-de92-48a1-8f93-d62afaa21b35"],

